    <text>
        <body>
            <div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1944-09-12T23:59:59-05:00"
                frus:doc-dateTime-min="1944-09-12T00:00:00-05:00" n="254"
                subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d254">
                <note rend="inline" type="source">
                    <gloss target="#t_JCS1">J.C.S.</gloss> Files</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">Memorandum by the United States Chiefs of Staff</hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#left">
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">top secret</hi>
                        <lb/>
                        <gloss target="#t_CCS1">C.C.S.</gloss> 674/1</seg>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">[<placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Quebec</hi>
                        </placeName>,] <date calendar="gregorian" when="1944-09-12">12 September
                            1944</date>.</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p rend="center">
                    <hi rend="smallcaps">Assumption of Command of “<gloss target="#t_Dragoon1"
                            >Dragoon</gloss>” Forces by Supreme Commander, Allied Expeditionary
                        Force</hi>
                </p>
                <p>The United States Chiefs of Staff recommend that the following message be sent to
                        <gloss target="#t_SCAEF1">SCAEF</gloss> and <gloss target="#t_SACMed1"
                        >SACMed</gloss> at once:<note n="1" xml:id="d254fn1">The dispatch of the
                        message quoted below was approved by the Combined Chiefs of Staff at their
                        172d Meeting, September 12, 1944. See <hi rend="italic">ante</hi>, <ref
                            target="#pg_306">p. 306</ref>. The message was sent as telegram No.
                            <gloss target="#t_Facs1">
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Facs</hi>
                        </gloss> 76.</note>
                </p>
                <quote rend="blockquote">
                    <p>“Effective 15 September <gloss target="#t_SCAEF1">SCAEF</gloss> will assume
                        command of <gloss target="#t_Dragoon1">
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Dragoon</hi>
                        </gloss> forces according to plan recommended in <gloss target="#t_Scaf1">
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Scaf</hi>
                        </gloss> 77.”<note n="2" xml:id="d254fn2">
                            <hi rend="italic">Ante</hi>, <ref target="#pg_232">p. 232</ref>.</note>
                    </p>
                </quote>
            </div>
        </body>
